{"tid":599876,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被搜出私煙後稱妻子所贈　休班警被判120小時服務令","createTime":"2018-03-20T23:52:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T12:43:36.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e2dc6e82e603a989fd112c396f4a93a44991fb91","tid":599876,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T23:52:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://passiontimes.hk/uploads/images/17156326_10210689014195014_4089963001755101771_n_1_2_5_6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F17156326_10210689014195014_4089963001755101771_n_1_2_5_6.jpg&h=478c99b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名休班警員，前年在深水埗街頭被警員截查時，於其背囊及膠袋搜出4200支私煙，被控一項管有應課稅品罪，早前被裁定罪成，今日（3月13日）在西九龍裁判法院被判120小時社會服務令。 <br />\n<br />\n辯方求情時指，指54歲被告林世全過往行為良好，而且有悔意，裁判官指報告顯示他已吸取教訓，可給予機會，故接納報告建議，判處社會服務令。 <br />\n<br />\n案情指，便衣海關關員在2016年11月28日在深水埗長沙灣道街頭，截查一名可疑男子，在其袋中搜出4200支私煙，後來更在其租用劏房單位搜出30萬支私煙，關員發現男子是休班警員。休班警指私煙是其妻所贈，又指劏房是其妻所住，雖然是他租用，但他沒有鎖匙。案中女被告早前認罪，被判入獄1年。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://passiontimes.hk/article/03-13-2018/44627\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F03-13-2018%2F44627&d=qGvFEy8J0bndsSsVQd2qMVKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=c5da61fc\" target=\"_blank\">http://passiontimes.hk/article/03-13-2018/44627</a>"},{"pid":"564739db28c54a856864d06587585c4daaf92eec","tid":599876,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T23:57:13.000Z","msg":"54歲當差都要住劏房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cc791eb273270b05f5847c338998f430d8f1203","tid":599876,"uid":70953,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T23:59:29.000Z","msg":"夫妻本是同林鳥大難來時各自飛"},{"pid":"a7bd12690dc365ff0294e2780023eb1f3043cbde","tid":599876,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"564739db28c54a856864d06587585c4daaf92eec","tid":599876,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-20